Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the Elizabeth "Liz" Kane-Leahy Memorial Highway
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the "Elizabeth 'Liz' Kane-Leahy Memorial Highway" on state route 208 in the county of Orange.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Elizabeth 'Liz' Kane-Leahy Memorial Highway"
